('ascending-triangle', 'Ascending Triangle Pattern', 'Bullish continuation pattern with flat resistance and rising support trendline.', 'The ascending triangle is a bullish continuation pattern characterized by a flat upper resistance line and a rising lower support line, indicating accumulating buying pressure.', 'Chart Patterns', 'intermediate', 10, ARRAY['triangle', 'continuation', 'bullish', 'breakout'], 'published', NOW()),
