('diamond-top', 'Diamond Top Pattern', 'Rare bearish reversal pattern combining broadening and triangle.', 'The diamond top is a rare but powerful bearish reversal pattern that forms at market tops, combining broadening and symmetrical triangle characteristics.', 'Chart Patterns', 'advanced', 15, ARRAY['reversal', 'bearish', 'rare', 'complex'], 'published', NOW()),
