('adx-indicator', 'ADX: Average Directional Index', 'Trend strength indicator regardless of direction.', 'The ADX measures trend strength without indicating direction, helping traders identify strong trends worth trading vs. ranging markets.', 'Technical Indicators', 'intermediate', 12, ARRAY['adx', 'trend-strength', 'directional', 'filtering'], 'published', NOW()),
