('parabolic-sar', 'Parabolic SAR Indicator', 'Trend-following indicator providing stop and reverse levels.', 'The Parabolic SAR provides potential entry and exit points by plotting dots above or below price based on trend direction.', 'Technical Indicators', 'intermediate', 12, ARRAY['parabolic', 'trend', 'stops', 'reversal'], 'published', NOW()),
